summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 6, 7, 8, 9 and 10, except the west 105 feet thereof and the vacated alley extending from Bothell Way to East 123rd St. between Bothell Way and 28th Avenue Northeast except the westerly half of such alley abutting to the rear the south one half of Lot 3 and Lots 4 and 5, all in Block 8, Homewood Park Addition, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-411 and 17-302, respectively.
